==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stiffness
<hw>Stiff"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
stiff; <as>as, the <ex>stiffness</ex> of cloth or of paste;
<ex>stiffness</ex> of manner; <ex>stiffness</ex> of
character.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The vices of old age have the <qex>stiffness</qex> of it too.</q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stifftail</ent>⟦br⟧
